	is able to chose either (in the main method)
	
	I dont remember if its either int[] mainAbilities or simply mainAbilities when using the method in Main
	
	check main abilities CheckStats(int[] mainAbilities)
	check side abilities CheckStats(int[] sideAbilities)
	or both abilities CheckStats{int[] mainAbilities, int [] sideAbilites)
	To make the information easier to read, add a print line of the abilitys names before using the CheckStats() method
	Example:
